{"tid":486205,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"水晶新手一問","createTime":"2017-12-01T15:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T00:27:58.000Z","uid":161174,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ab4e69fe9c9daa8631fa526609cf93833b2d24","tid":486205,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"話說最近淘宝買左條綠幽靈比自己，第一次養水晶，睇左好多有關水晶消磁既資料。<br />\n見綠幽靈好似3個月左右消一次就ok，原本已經計劃好買白水晶既消磁石每日訓教同番工放係上面養住佢，費時亂放。我咁期待，花左爛左我會喊嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後每3個月先浸佢一次水，淨化佢，唔知呢個方法對唔對，求各路師兄師姐指點下小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我估你地會屌我買水晶都買淘宝野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但純粹嘗試一下，簡價錢同合眼緣都簡左我好奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，希望唔好令我失望<br />\n話說，我雙11 D野都未黎，已經幾日啦，集運仲未開始運啊，屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好鬼心急想見我條水晶晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水晶黎左就影張相記錄下，聽講會越養越綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8b3d151163c52892cdcfb38ca0b039e757c665","tid":486205,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"新人第一次開post ,唔好做留言終結者啦希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a50406b911c7ae3404e36b4e0bcef4afdb22ab","tid":486205,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"[img]adf1db00864b2aa71ba206371c518a2a.jpg[/img]<br />\n其實我簡左好奈好多間，先問老板娘拎相睇。我地呢D窮書生邊有錢買正野啊，老板娘都幾好人啊，一張張咁send比我。第一張就比我睇中左佢，可以話一見鍾情。之後睇多幾張都係呢條合我眼緣同荷包緣，既然有緣就簡佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實綠幽靈真係好燃貴，希望佢旺下我個荷包啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢條唔算貴，平平地玩下先，好玩就睇下買唔買其佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003e92cca40bc1f78c75340e41e1c50cb4dca49d","tid":486205,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/000133_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F000133_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=66a6bca9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38209ea999d05a441f5b7805fcb8e147e5f6848e","tid":486205,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]adf1db00864b2aa71ba206371c518a2a.jpg[/img]<br />\n其實我簡左好奈好多間，先問老板娘拎相睇。我地呢D窮書生邊有錢買正野啊，老板娘都幾好人啊，一張張咁send比我。第一張就比我睇中左佢，可以話一見鍾情。之後睇多幾張都係呢條合我眼緣同荷包緣，既然有緣就簡佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實綠幽靈真係好燃貴，希望佢旺下我個荷包啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢條唔算貴，平平地玩下先，好玩就睇下買唔買其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"502f9280cc30f336decf49d39d00d08eacfc71a3","tid":486205,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84681a7dd9dfe0e657029b1489c589ca886fedd","tid":486205,"uid":11662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:09:35.000Z","msg":"唔浸水㗎喎，放上白晶簇已經係淨化<br />\n最好買埋紫晶簇啦"},{"pid":"a08a247e9056e1f76cb3d61cdabc8959af244d61","tid":486205,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T00:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔浸水㗎喎，放上白晶簇已經係淨化<br />\n最好買埋紫晶簇啦</blockquote><br />\n咁可唔可以日日都放係上面？唔想亂放，我係平平地買白水晶消磁石炸<br />\n浸水係想清理一下佢表面，唔想影響佢成色<br />\n見人地話用御守鹽，雖然平平地，但怕自己唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}